re service. Further, it offers AltaSigna Enterprise, a document creation, signing, and distribution application; AltaSigna Maple, an automated signing and verification tool; and AltaSigna Pine, an e-mandate signature and verification solution. Additionally, it offers Crypta Vault that tokenizes and secures sensitive data. The company was incorporated in 1990 and is headquartered in Chennai, India."}}